              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " One germanium- lithium detector is  used with",
                "an active volume of  63 cm**3 and a resolution of 3.0",
                "keV at Eg=1.33 MeV.The gamma-rays were detected  at",
                "angles of 0, 30, 45, 60 and 90 degrees in the",
                "laboratory system.  The detector was calibrated",
                "using gamma-rays  from reaction 27Al(p,gamma)28Si at",
                "proton energy 991.86(3)keV. For reduction of the",
                "background from low energy gamma-rays the detector was",
                " shielded with Pb and Cu."
